resources.string: The dream is mine, why not?!
Cowards never try, losers never end, and winners never give up!
I believed in myself when no one else did!
In my car there will always be a space for whoever was beside me on the bus.
Pain abuses but builds unshakable shields.
I\'d rather take the risk of doing something I love, rather than feel lost for not doing what I love.
Be awesome, the world is full of 7 notes!
Failure is not falling, it is refusing to get up.
If she wanted you in failure, she deserves you in success!
Go around, but don\'t go over people.
